| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-2864 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4ac2e186-f484-5060-9a8a-05a1917cb3c1"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
